dct_title_s: Map of the tectonic units of Syria
dct_description_sm: Geological Institute of the Russian Academy of Sciences. Geological Survey of Israel. Companion text: Tectonics / Vladimir G. Kazmin. Geological framework of the Levant. Volume I: Cyprus and Syria / Valerie A. Krqasheninnikov; John K. Hall; Francis Hirsch; Chaim Benjamini. Jerusalem: Historical Productions-Hall. 2005. 463-498 p. Article is chapter 8. North Decimal Degree 37.3333. South Decimal Degree 32.300. East Decimal Degree 42.4167. West Decimal Degree 35.700. Map is plate IIa. Mercator projection, Pulkovo 1942 datum.
